---
import CheckmarkIcon from "@icons/checkmark-blue.svg";
---

<section class="section-dark">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>What Sets Apex Attics Apart</h2>
        <p>
            We’re more than just attic converters. We’re your trusted local team
            committed to delivering storage solutions that add real value to
            your home.
        </p>

        <div class="list">
            <div class="card">
                <CheckmarkIcon />
                <h3>Skilled and Friendly Team</h3>
                <p>
                    Our crew brings years of experience and a friendly attitude
                    to every job. We focus on detail, safety, and customer
                    satisfaction from start to finish.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <CheckmarkIcon />
                <h3>5-Year Quality Guarantee</h3>
                <p>
                    Each attic storage project is covered by our 5-year
                    workmanship warranty. We use premium materials and proven
                    methods to ensure a safe and lasting result.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <CheckmarkIcon />
                <h3>Client-First Approach</h3>
                <p>
                    We make it easy. You’ll enjoy clear updates, helpful support
                    and a smooth experience from your first quote to final
                    inspection.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <CheckmarkIcon />
                <h3>Tailored to Suit You</h3>
                <p>
                    We offer flexible conversion options and schedule jobs
                    around your availability, making sure the process fits your
                    home and lifestyle.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <CheckmarkIcon />
                <h3>Smart Use of Space</h3>
                <p>
                    Our attic solutions help you reclaim your home. By turning
                    unused roof space into functional storage, we free up floor
                    space and make everyday living easier.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .container > h2,
    .container > p {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 3rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .card {
        padding: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>
